{"tid":2069214,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"(轉貼:)【老師傅】先達整機佬維修電話30年 電話入水,充唔到電可以點處理?","createTime":"2020-06-18T08:32:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T16:05:01.000Z","uid":131616,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"71e42bcb31599c964d23d6d16f3084b2a0c1b9c5","tid":2069214,"uid":131616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T08:32:33.000Z","msg":"【玩物達人】<br />\n作為科技記者，每次寫先達廣場都有網民留言：先達佬，信唔過。且慢負評！先達作為香港多年的標誌性電話商場，也存在着不少奇人趣事，其中對着男廁的電話維修店門口大大隻字寫着「廁所勿問」，感覺甚有殺氣，58歲的老師傅黃xx（Wilson）已有30年的維修電話經驗，最有資格分享「整機佬」這個行業。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wTdRCbrQL4s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwTdRCbrQL4s&d=j4yDeGq49jMu68ZzGhcJHnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=93427cd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wTdRCbrQL4s</a>"},{"pid":"bbb629f05d747820c5f9fcb14648f41be9df9272","tid":2069214,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T08:34:08.000Z","msg":"由功能電話整到智能電話咁與時并進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83fe4850259f9a3ad6ed35f6a81a7f5a777d09aa","tid":2069214,"uid":59920,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bbb629f05d747820c5f9fcb14648f41be9df9272","tid":2069214,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T08:34:08.000Z","msg":"由功能電話整到智能電話咁與時并進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T08:44:18.000Z","msg":